public class MyModelConverter : IModelConverter<MyModel, LinqToSqlModel>\n{\n    public MyModel ConvertToDomain(LinqToSqlModel item)\n    {\n        return new MyModel\n        {\n            Id = item.Id,\n            Name = item.Name\n            // Map other properties as needed\n        };\n    }\n\n    public LinqToSqlModel ConvertToLinq(MyModel item)\n    {\n        return new LinqToSqlModel\n        {\n            Id = item.Id,\n            Name = item.Name\n            // Map other properties as needed\n        };\n    }\n}